title: Setup
---
// Declaring variables to be used later
<<declare $visitedJeff = false>>
<<declare $foundWrench= false>>
===
title: OptionsGuy
---
//The node has to relate to the character's name.
//Nothing stopping there being multiple dialog files!
OptionsGuy: Hi there!
OptionsGuy: I'm just here to test the Options system
->  Looks like it's working.
    OptionsGuy: Well, that's good to know
->  I think it's still broken.
    OptionsGuy: That's annoying!

